activities: StayWell gathers names, addresses, dates of birth, email addresses, phone numbers, chronic disease information, and other information regarding individuals' health and health-related behaviors to provide comprehensive health management programs for individuals.  Using the information voluntarily collected from each individual, StayWell offers a health assessment, and provides tailored feedback, health information, and educational tools and resources on health behaviors and diseases and conditions.
personaldata: Offline, Online, and Manually Processed Data
privacyprograms: StayWell is an early adopter of the NCQA wellness certification standards, and NCQA certification has been issued.
